   2. Add as external source, then "Generate blocks from source"
   3. Verify Setpoint flags and comments on a sample member

 Hierarchy depth from DB root to leaf:
   DB -> units[] -> modules[] -> valves[] -> *Limits -> hiLimit  (5 levels)

